│ The `planContainsAdditionalSimplifications` function checks if the VPlan      │
│ contains additional simplifications not accounted for in the legacy cost      │
│ model. It does this by comparing the instructions in the loop with those in   │
│ the VPlan. If there are instructions in the loop that are not part of the     │
│ VPlan or are skipped for cost computation, the function returns `true`,       │
│ indicating that the VPlan has additional simplifications.                     │
│                                                                               │
│ The issue likely arises because the function does not fully account for all   │
│ scenarios where the VPlan and the legacy cost model might disagree. To        │
│ address this, we can enhance the logic in                                     │
│ `planContainsAdditionalSimplifications` to ensure it accurately identifies    │
│ cases where the VPlan contains valid simplifications.                         │
│                                                                               │
│ ### Proposed Fix                                                              │
│                                                                               │
│ We will modify the `planContainsAdditionalSimplifications` function to        │
│ include additional checks for instructions that might be skipped or           │
│ simplified differently in the VPlan. This will ensure that the function       │
│ provides a more accurate assessment of whether the VPlan contains additional  │
│ simplifications.                                                              │
│                                                                               │
│ ### Next Steps                                                                │
│                                                                               │
│ I will edit the `planContainsAdditionalSimplifications` function to implement │
│ the proposed fix.                                                             │
